query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(tq1 t1) NoHashJoin(t1 tq1 q1) NoMergeJoin(q1 t1 tq1 a1) NoMergeJoin(a1 acc q1 t1 tq1 u1 b) NoMergeJoin(a1 acc b q1 t1 tq1 u1 s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('cordova',
'jframe',
'node.js',
'package',
'raspberry-pi',
'ssis',
'substring',
'vector',
'yii2')
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name ilike '%tax%'
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow');
